8ca5f3f4-d307-46b7-b842-fde4a747b211.title: Mazrion
8ca5f3f4-d307-46b7-b842-fde4a747b211.text: Please leave me alone, a parrot stole my banana.

59ecc4b0-9831-4b7a-8817-db231185da7f.title: <player>
59ecc4b0-9831-4b7a-8817-db231185da7f.text: Uhh... How do you know my name?

eae821d8-d509-42b3-b5a4-01db58af3754.title: Mazion
eae821d8-d509-42b3-b5a4-01db58af3754.text: Oh, I like to keep ahead of things.

c136f01a-b981-4417-8d95-754e4d382928.title: <player>
c136f01a-b981-4417-8d95-754e4d382928.text:
Err.. ok. Well, I've been sent from the Wizards' Guild
in Yanille. There's been an... incident... Do you have
any body parts?

aa321dfa-8474-4d59-84b0-0eb3efa63eda.title: Mazion
aa321dfa-8474-4d59-84b0-0eb3efa63eda.text:
How did you know! I found the most awful thing in my
sandpit - a head!

be633762-b980-4d53-856b-fe06ac9001ca.title: <player>
be633762-b980-4d53-856b-fe06ac9001ca.text: Ahhh good! I need to take it back to be buried!

0f1648dd-b6e0-4551-b01c-2dca1eb0724d.title: Mazion
0f1648dd-b6e0-4551-b01c-2dca1eb0724d.text:
You're very strange, but if it means I get rid of the
horrid thing...

fa30b115-26ba-44d8-8fee-2f6cbc96bb4d.title: Mazion
fa30b115-26ba-44d8-8fee-2f6cbc96bb4d.text:
I see you still have that head! Take it back to the
Wizards in Yanille!

fec6a8f3-7c82-426c-9bfd-1fcf29f56093.title: <player>
fec6a8f3-7c82-426c-9bfd-1fcf29f56093.text: What should I do with the head?

49730614-ad79-4780-ac1d-6598263df5d2.title: Mazion
49730614-ad79-4780-ac1d-6598263df5d2.text:
It was you that came demanding the head to give to
the wizard in the first place! Go back to Yanille with it!

options.text: What should I do with the head?

b22a4039-1c5e-4421-8e55-7e79c14cbbf7.title: Mazion
b22a4039-1c5e-4421-8e55-7e79c14cbbf7.text:
Keep your hair on! You dropped it! Make sure you
take it straight back to the wizards else you won't have
a leg to stand on.
